Miguel was last seen on July 17 in the presence of Ebrahim at a KFC near his grandmother's home in Sydenham.
Following an extensive search for the youngster, private security guards discovered his body while chasing suspects involved in an armed robbery. 
Miguel's body was discovered buried in a shallow grave in Longbury Drive in Phoenix in September. 

His funeral was held at the St Anne's church in Randles Road, days later. 
Ebrahim has been taken to the Durban Central police station, where he will be charged. 
